"{\"uid\": \"theatlantic.com-family-archive-2024-08-adult-gymnastics-olympics-679314\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Competitors in the sport are getting older, transforming the image of a gymnast from meek little girl to empowered athlete.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 123, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Competitors\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 11}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 15, \"to\": 24}, {\"ngram\": \"the image\", \"from\": 57, \"to\": 66}, {\"ngram\": \"a gymnast\", \"from\": 70, \"to\": 79}, {\"ngram\": \"meek little girl\", \"from\": 85, \"to\": 101}, {\"ngram\": \"athlete\", \"from\": 115, \"to\": 122}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2016, the two-time Olympic gymnast Aly Raisman was known for her incredible floor routine \\u2026 and penchant for naps.\", \"from\": 125, \"to\": 242, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 163, \"end\": 174, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aly_Raisman\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Aly Raisman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aly_Raisman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aly_Raisman\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"In 2016, the two-time Olympic gymnast\", \"from\": 125, \"to\": 162}, {\"ngram\": \"her incredible floor routine\", \"from\": 189, \"to\": 217}, {\"ngram\": \"naps\", \"from\": 237, \"to\": 241}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Raisman, the oldest member of the team, took the chance to snooze whenever she could get it.\", \"from\": 243, \"to\": 335, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Raisman\", \"from\": 243, \"to\": 250}, {\"ngram\": \"the oldest member\", \"from\": 252, \"to\": 269}, {\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 273, \"to\": 281}, {\"ngram\": \"the chance\", \"from\": 288, \"to\": 298}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Simone Biles jokingly called her \\\"our sleeping little grandma.\\\"\", \"from\": 336, \"to\": 399, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Simone Biles\", \"from\": 336, \"to\": 348}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"our sleeping little grandma\", \"from\": 369, \"to\": 397}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Raisman was 22 years old.\", \"from\": 400, \"to\": 425, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Raisman\", \"from\": 400, \"to\": 407}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So, you know, ancient.\", \"from\": 426, \"to\": 448, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"By 2021, at the Tokyo Olympics, Biles was 24 and had earned the \\\"grandma\\\" nickname herself.\", \"from\": 450, \"to\": 541, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Tokyo Olympics\", \"from\": 462, \"to\": 480}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 482, \"to\": 487}, {\"ngram\": \"the \\\"grandma\", \"from\": 510, \"to\": 522}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This year, Biles is 27, she's competing at her third Olympics, and the average age of an athlete on the U.S. women's gymnastics team is about22 and a half.\", \"from\": 542, \"to\": 697, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 553, \"to\": 558}, {\"ngram\": \"her third Olympics\", \"from\": 585, \"to\": 603}, {\"ngram\": \"the average age\", \"from\": 609, \"to\": 624}, {\"ngram\": \"an athlete\", \"from\": 628, \"to\": 638}, {\"ngram\": \"the U.S. women's gymnastics team\", \"from\": 642, \"to\": 674}, {\"ngram\": \"about22\", \"from\": 678, \"to\": 685}, {\"ngram\": \"a half\", \"from\": 690, \"to\": 696}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bilesrecently apologized to Raisman, saying that she's learned what it's like to be a \\\"grandma.\\\"\", \"from\": 698, \"to\": 794, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Raisman\", \"from\": 726, \"to\": 733}, {\"ngram\": \"a \\\"grandma\", \"from\": 782, \"to\": 792}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her body hurts more.\", \"from\": 795, \"to\": 815, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Her body\", \"from\": 795, \"to\": 803}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She needs more rest after competitions.\", \"from\": 816, \"to\": 855, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"more rest\", \"from\": 826, \"to\": 835}, {\"ngram\": \"competitions\", \"from\": 842, \"to\": 854}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And I have to say: I feel her pain.\", \"from\": 856, \"to\": 891, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her pain\", \"from\": 882, \"to\": 890}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I myself am a gymnast-and I am turning 40 this year.\", \"from\": 893, \"to\": 945, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a gymnast\", \"from\": 905, \"to\": 914}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Unfortunately,I did not make the 2024 Olympic Team.\", \"from\": 946, \"to\": 997, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Olympic Team\", \"from\": 975, \"to\": 996}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am watching all those grandma gymnasts from home, with my adult gymnastics squad.\", \"from\": 998, \"to\": 1081, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all those grandma gymnasts\", \"from\": 1012, \"to\": 1038}, {\"ngram\": \"home\", \"from\": 1044, \"to\": 1048}, {\"ngram\": \"my adult gymnastics squad\", \"from\": 1055, \"to\": 1080}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The youngest among us are in their 20s; the oldest is in her 50s.\", \"from\": 1082, \"to\": 1147, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1101, \"to\": 1103}, {\"ngram\": \"their 20s\", \"from\": 1111, \"to\": 1120}, {\"ngram\": \"her 50s\", \"from\": 1139, \"to\": 1146}]}, {\"sentence\": \"About half of the team had never done gymnastics before joining this class.\", \"from\": 1148, \"to\": 1223, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"About half\", \"from\": 1148, \"to\": 1158}, {\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 1162, \"to\": 1170}, {\"ngram\": \"gymnastics\", \"from\": 1186, \"to\": 1196}, {\"ngram\": \"this class\", \"from\": 1212, \"to\": 1222}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We train together two days a week and compete a few times a year.\", \"from\": 1224, \"to\": 1289, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"At our gym, when the little girls learn new skills, they get a beaded jewel.\", \"from\": 1290, \"to\": 1366, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our gym\", \"from\": 1293, \"to\": 1300}, {\"ngram\": \"the little girls\", \"from\": 1307, \"to\": 1323}, {\"ngram\": \"new skills\", \"from\": 1330, \"to\": 1340}, {\"ngram\": \"a beaded jewel\", \"from\": 1351, \"to\": 1365}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When we do, we win an Advil.\", \"from\": 1367, \"to\": 1395, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an Advil\", \"from\": 1386, \"to\": 1394}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We need more naps than Raisman or Biles, but you could not pay us to stay home from class.\", \"from\": 1396, \"to\": 1486, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"more naps\", \"from\": 1404, \"to\": 1413}, {\"ngram\": \"Raisman\", \"from\": 1419, \"to\": 1426}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 1430, \"to\": 1435}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1459, \"to\": 1461}, {\"ngram\": \"class\", \"from\": 1480, \"to\": 1485}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the past decade, interest in adult gymnastics has exploded, coinciding with the growing age of champions around the world.\", \"from\": 1488, \"to\": 1613, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the past decade\", \"from\": 1491, \"to\": 1506}, {\"ngram\": \"interest\", \"from\": 1508, \"to\": 1516}, {\"ngram\": \"adult gymnastics\", \"from\": 1520, \"to\": 1536}, {\"ngram\": \"the growing age\", \"from\": 1567, \"to\": 1582}, {\"ngram\": \"champions\", \"from\": 1586, \"to\": 1595}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1603, \"to\": 1612}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For years, successful female gymnaststraditionally peakedat 15 or 16 years old.\", \"from\": 1614, \"to\": 1693, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"years\", \"from\": 1618, \"to\": 1623}, {\"ngram\": \"successful female\", \"from\": 1625, \"to\": 1642}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Many trained under abusive conditions.\", \"from\": 1694, \"to\": 1732, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"abusive conditions\", \"from\": 1713, \"to\": 1731}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They competed for their coaches or their countries, not themselves.\", \"from\": 1733, \"to\": 1800, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their coaches\", \"from\": 1751, \"to\": 1764}, {\"ngram\": \"their countries\", \"from\": 1768, \"to\": 1783}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But now gymnastics isdominatedby women in their mid- to late 20s (and even early 30s) who want to win on their own terms.\", \"from\": 1801, \"to\": 1922, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"But now gymnastics isdominatedby women\", \"from\": 1801, \"to\": 1839}, {\"ngram\": \"their mid-\", \"from\": 1843, \"to\": 1853}, {\"ngram\": \"late 20s\", \"from\": 1857, \"to\": 1865}, {\"ngram\": \"even early 30s\", \"from\": 1871, \"to\": 1885}, {\"ngram\": \"their own terms\", \"from\": 1906, \"to\": 1921}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Their longevity is inspiring more grown-ups, both amateur and professional, to return to the sport-and encouraging others, who might never have thought gymnastics would welcome them, to learn to flip too.\", \"from\": 1923, \"to\": 2127, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Their longevity\", \"from\": 1923, \"to\": 1938}, {\"ngram\": \"more grown-ups\", \"from\": 1952, \"to\": 1966}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport-and encouraging others\", \"from\": 2012, \"to\": 2044}, {\"ngram\": \"gymnastics\", \"from\": 2075, \"to\": 2085}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Unlike me, Stacey Tirro did not do gymnastics as a child.\", \"from\": 2129, \"to\": 2186, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2140, \"end\": 2146, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stacey_Slater\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1579425734938102e-28, \"text\": \"Stacey\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stacey_Slater\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stacey_Slater\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"gymnastics\", \"from\": 2164, \"to\": 2174}, {\"ngram\": \"a child\", \"from\": 2178, \"to\": 2185}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But when she saw the joy on her kids' faces as they bounced on a trampoline in their gymnastics classes, she decided she also wanted to experience that.\", \"from\": 2187, \"to\": 2339, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the joy\", \"from\": 2204, \"to\": 2211}, {\"ngram\": \"her kids' faces\", \"from\": 2215, \"to\": 2230}, {\"ngram\": \"a trampoline\", \"from\": 2250, \"to\": 2262}, {\"ngram\": \"their gymnastics classes\", \"from\": 2266, \"to\": 2290}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So what if she was 36, practically dead in gymnastics years?\", \"from\": 2340, \"to\": 2400, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"gymnastics years\", \"from\": 2383, \"to\": 2399}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2008, she worked up the courage to join that gym's adult class.\", \"from\": 2401, \"to\": 2467, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the courage\", \"from\": 2424, \"to\": 2435}, {\"ngram\": \"that gym's adult class\", \"from\": 2444, \"to\": 2466}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She's been tracking her progress under the name \\\"The Geriatric Gymnast\\\" ever since.\", \"from\": 2468, \"to\": 2551, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her progress\", \"from\": 2488, \"to\": 2500}, {\"ngram\": \"the name\", \"from\": 2507, \"to\": 2515}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"The Geriatric Gymnast\", \"from\": 2516, \"to\": 2538}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tirro was lucky there was a class to join at all.\", \"from\": 2553, \"to\": 2602, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tirro\", \"from\": 2553, \"to\": 2558}, {\"ngram\": \"a class\", \"from\": 2579, \"to\": 2586}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the early 2010s, grown-up gymnasts were pretty much on their own.\", \"from\": 2603, \"to\": 2671, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the early 2010s\", \"from\": 2606, \"to\": 2621}, {\"ngram\": \"grown-up gymnasts\", \"from\": 2623, \"to\": 2640}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Insurance for adult classes is expensive, so the most common options were \\\"open gym sessions\\\"-essentially, loosely supervised free-for-alls where you could bounce on the trampoline and launch yourself into the foam pit, but where you would not necessarily learn much.\", \"from\": 2672, \"to\": 2939, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Insurance\", \"from\": 2672, \"to\": 2681}, {\"ngram\": \"adult classes\", \"from\": 2686, \"to\": 2699}, {\"ngram\": \"the most common options\", \"from\": 2717, \"to\": 2740}, {\"ngram\": \"open gym\", \"from\": 2747, \"to\": 2755}, {\"ngram\": \"free-for-alls\", \"from\": 2798, \"to\": 2811}, {\"ngram\": \"the trampoline\", \"from\": 2838, \"to\": 2852}, {\"ngram\": \"the foam pit\", \"from\": 2878, \"to\": 2890}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gina Paulhus, who was in her 20s at the time, did take classes but told me she had to train with high-school girls.\", \"from\": 2940, \"to\": 3055, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2940, \"end\": 2944, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Characters_of_Holby_City\", \"score\": 0.9324602302599436, \"rank\": 0.07243179660471392, \"text\": \"Gina\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Characters_of_Holby_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Characters_of_Holby_City\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her 20s\", \"from\": 2965, \"to\": 2972}, {\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 2976, \"to\": 2984}, {\"ngram\": \"classes\", \"from\": 2995, \"to\": 3002}, {\"ngram\": \"high-school girls\", \"from\": 3037, \"to\": 3054}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Eager to find gymnasts her own age, she started a Facebook group called \\\"Just like fine wine \\u2026 Adult Gymnastics Group\\\" in 2014.\", \"from\": 3056, \"to\": 3183, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3157, \"end\": 3167, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gymnastics\", \"score\": 0.9999993647126957, \"rank\": 6.352880039295107e-07, \"text\": \"Gymnastics\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gymnastics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gymnastics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"gymnasts\", \"from\": 3070, \"to\": 3078}, {\"ngram\": \"her own age\", \"from\": 3079, \"to\": 3090}, {\"ngram\": \"a Facebook group\", \"from\": 3104, \"to\": 3120}, {\"ngram\": \"fine wine\", \"from\": 3139, \"to\": 3148}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She later founded anAdult Gymnastics Camp.\", \"from\": 3184, \"to\": 3226, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3210, \"end\": 3220, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gymnastics\", \"score\": 0.9999993647126957, \"rank\": 6.352880039295107e-07, \"text\": \"Gymnastics\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gymnastics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gymnastics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But Tirro and Paulhus were outliers.\", \"from\": 3227, \"to\": 3263, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tirro\", \"from\": 3231, \"to\": 3236}, {\"ngram\": \"Paulhus\", \"from\": 3241, \"to\": 3248}, {\"ngram\": \"outliers\", \"from\": 3254, \"to\": 3262}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In general, serious gymnastics-the kind where you go and learn skills and try to get better-was still just for kids.\", \"from\": 3264, \"to\": 3380, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"general, serious gymnastics\", \"from\": 3267, \"to\": 3294}, {\"ngram\": \"the kind\", \"from\": 3295, \"to\": 3303}, {\"ngram\": \"skills\", \"from\": 3327, \"to\": 3333}, {\"ngram\": \"kids\", \"from\": 3375, \"to\": 3379}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's largely because, starting in the 1970s, coaches in America perceived \\\"little girls in pretty boxes\\\" as more trainable than adults.\", \"from\": 3382, \"to\": 3519, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 1970s\", \"from\": 3418, \"to\": 3427}, {\"ngram\": \"coaches\", \"from\": 3429, \"to\": 3436}, {\"ngram\": \"America\", \"from\": 3440, \"to\": 3447}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"little girls\", \"from\": 3458, \"to\": 3471}, {\"ngram\": \"pretty boxes\", \"from\": 3475, \"to\": 3487}, {\"ngram\": \"adults\", \"from\": 3512, \"to\": 3518}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Well into the 2010s, a brutal coaching culture remained: Keep 'em weak, keep 'em hungry, keep 'em doubtful and dependent.\", \"from\": 3520, \"to\": 3641, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 2010s\", \"from\": 3530, \"to\": 3539}, {\"ngram\": \"a brutal coaching culture\", \"from\": 3541, \"to\": 3566}, {\"ngram\": \"'em\", \"from\": 3582, \"to\": 3585}, {\"ngram\": \"'em\", \"from\": 3597, \"to\": 3600}, {\"ngram\": \"'em\", \"from\": 3614, \"to\": 3617}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That, the conventional wisdom went, was the only way to win.\", \"from\": 3642, \"to\": 3702, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the conventional wisdom\", \"from\": 3648, \"to\": 3671}, {\"ngram\": \"the only way\", \"from\": 3682, \"to\": 3694}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Girls did what they were told-and when they were too physically or mentally broken, they were disposed of.\", \"from\": 3703, \"to\": 3809, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Girls\", \"from\": 3703, \"to\": 3708}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The long line of little girls desperate to go to the Olympics never ended, after all.\", \"from\": 3810, \"to\": 3895, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The long line\", \"from\": 3810, \"to\": 3823}, {\"ngram\": \"little girls\", \"from\": 3827, \"to\": 3839}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 3859, \"to\": 3871}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This culture was set in part by the most notorious coaches of the modern era: B\\u00e9la and M\\u00e1rta K\\u00e1rolyi.\", \"from\": 3897, \"to\": 3998, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3984, \"end\": 3997, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/M\\u00e1rta_K\\u00e1rolyi\", \"score\": 0.9999999991350705, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"M\\u00e1rta K\\u00e1rolyi\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/M\\u00e1rta_K\\u00e1rolyi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/M\\u00e1rta_K\\u00e1rolyi\"}], \"noun_phras