igationcommissioned by the U.S. Olympic & Paralympic Committee, no parents were allowed there during training camps.\", \"from\": 4487, \"to\": 4636, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"toan independent\", \"from\": 4497, \"to\": 4513}, {\"ngram\": \"the U.S. Olympic & Paralympic Committee\", \"from\": 4543, \"to\": 4582}, {\"ngram\": \"no parents\", \"from\": 4584, \"to\": 4594}, {\"ngram\": \"training camps\", \"from\": 4621, \"to\": 4635}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles has said that she and other underfed gymnastsbroke into the cafeteria at nightto steal food.\", \"from\": 4637, \"to\": 4735, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 4637, \"to\": 4642}, {\"ngram\": \"the cafeteria\", \"from\": 4699, \"to\": 4712}, {\"ngram\": \"nightto steal food\", \"from\": 4716, \"to\": 4734}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Ranch was also whereseveral gymnasts saythe former national-team doctor Larry Nassar sexually abused them under the guise of medical care.\", \"from\": 4736, \"to\": 4878, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4736, \"end\": 4745, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Ranch\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.350644833819642e-23, \"text\": \"The Ranch\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Ranch\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Ranch\"}, {\"begin\": 4812, \"end\": 4824, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Larry_Nassar\", \"score\": 0.9986437956255909, \"rank\": 0.0013580461622554245, \"text\": \"Larry Nassar\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q2159907\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Larry_Nassar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Larry_Nassar\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"whereseveral gymnasts\", \"from\": 4755, \"to\": 4776}, {\"ngram\": \"the guise\", \"from\": 4852, \"to\": 4861}, {\"ngram\": \"medical care\", \"from\": 4865, \"to\": 4877}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(M\\u00e1rta later saidthat she felt \\\"extremely bad\\\" about Nassar's abuse but that she did not \\\"feel responsible.\\\"\", \"from\": 4879, \"to\": 4987, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4932, \"end\": 4938, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Larry_Nassar\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.2370811093971042e-79, \"text\": \"Nassar\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q2159907\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Larry_Nassar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Larry_Nassar\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"M\\u00e1rta\", \"from\": 4880, \"to\": 4885}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The K\\u00e1rolyisalso denied claimsthat they themselves were abusive.)\", \"from\": 4988, \"to\": 5053, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The K\\u00e1rolyisalso\", \"from\": 4988, \"to\": 5004}, {\"ngram\": \"claimsthat\", \"from\": 5012, \"to\": 5022}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This culture trickled down, and coaches around the country modeled their practices after the K\\u00e1rolyis.\", \"from\": 5055, \"to\": 5157, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This culture\", \"from\": 5055, \"to\": 5067}, {\"ngram\": \"coaches\", \"from\": 5087, \"to\": 5094}, {\"ngram\": \"the country\", \"from\": 5102, \"to\": 5113}, {\"ngram\": \"their practices\", \"from\": 5122, \"to\": 5137}, {\"ngram\": \"the K\\u00e1rolyis\", \"from\": 5144, \"to\": 5156}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Many believed the lie that broken bones and broken spirits weresigns of hard work.\", \"from\": 5158, \"to\": 5240, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the lie\", \"from\": 5172, \"to\": 5179}, {\"ngram\": \"hard work\", \"from\": 5230, \"to\": 5239}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As a kid, my teammates and I never rose to the level of Biles or Raisman.\", \"from\": 5241, \"to\": 5314, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a kid\", \"from\": 5244, \"to\": 5249}, {\"ngram\": \"my teammates\", \"from\": 5251, \"to\": 5263}, {\"ngram\": \"the level\", \"from\": 5284, \"to\": 5293}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"fr